He further said about 46 million US Dollars will be spend this
year by the tribunal to facilitate its work.
</P>
<P>
The ICTR was established in November, 1994 by the Security
Council Resolution 955 to prosecute persons responsible for
genocide and other serious violations of international
humanitarian law committed in Rwanda.
