with trafficking and marketing of 691.6 g of drugs, hiding 11.60 g
of No.3 heroin, and 1.6 g of "ice" in their home. The two were
arrested by local police.
</P>
<P>
The court also announced its final ruling on 40 of 43 people
found guilty in 23 separate cases at a special anti-drug meeting
held in a local stadium yesterday. 
