<HEADLINE> PLA Delegation Leaves for Visit to Three European Nations </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 7 (Xinhua) -- A delegation of the Chinese
People's Liberation Army (PLA) led by Li Laizhu, commander of the
