</P>
<P>
"I have asked the Indian prime minister that troops should be
withdrawn from Kashmir as a first gesture which will help in
building an atmosphere of trust," Sharif said in an interview with
a private Indian television, El-TV, here last week, sources from
the Prime Minister's Secretariat said today.
</P>
<P>
The prime minister, however, conceded that there are
limitations on both sides.
</P>
<P>
