<HEADLINE> Major News Items in Leading Egyptian Newspapers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CAIRO, June 7 (Xinhua) -- The following are major news items
in leading Egyptian newspapers today:
</P>
<P>
Al-Ahram:
</P>
<P>
-- Egyptian President Hosni Mubarak and Palestinian National
Authority (PNA) President Yasser Arafat will discuss a latest
five-point proposal for resuming negotiations between the
Palestinians and Israelis.
</P>
